o use. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Updox, for example, lets a doctor <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Schedule an appointment <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Receive a patient&#8217;s medical history <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Review lab results <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Send a secure message <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. Get paid Doximity has a similar feature set.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Doctors spend most of their time writing prescriptions. So what to look for when picking a prescription app?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What makes a good prescription?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/plainswipe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/DALL\u00b7E-2022-11-10-16.59.51-a-dog-dressed-as-a-patient-receiving-a-prescription-from-a-doctor.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-805\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A good digital prescription should be clear, concise, and easy to read. It should also include all of the necessary information for the patient, such as the name and dosage of the medication, the route of administration, and the frequency and duration of treatment.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Why do prescription apps make the best online consultations app for doctors?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>There are many reasons why prescription apps make the best online consultations app for doctors. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/plainswipe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/DALL\u00b7E-2022-11-10-17.02.20-a-mad-patient-calling-a-doctor-to-schedule-an-appointment-and-fill-out-their-medical-history-digital-art.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-806\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>First, they are convenient for both doctors and patients. Patients can easily schedule an appointment and fill out their medical history online. This saves time for both the doctor and the patient. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Second, prescription apps make it easy for doctors to keep track of their patients\u2019 medical history. They can easily see what medications the patient is taking and whether they are having any side effects. This information is important for the doctor to know in order to provide the best care possible. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/plainswipe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/DALL\u00b7E-2022-11-10-17.04.16-a-happy-doctor-dressed-as-Sherlock-homes-tracking-his-patients-history.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-807\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Third, prescription apps allow doctors to prescribe medications directly to their patients. This is convenient for both the doctor and the patient. The patient does not have to go to the pharmacy to pick up their prescription. The doctor can also be sure that the patient is taking the correct medication. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Fourth, prescription apps make it easy for doctors to monitor their patients\u2019 progress. They can see how well the patient is responding to the medication and make changes if necessary. This helps the doctor to provide the best care possible. Overall, prescription apps make the best online consultations app for doctors.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To try a great prescription app, go to prescription writer on PlainSwipe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/plainswipe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/DALL\u00b7E-2022-11-10-17.06.33-doctor-dressed-as-batman-dictating-a-prescription-and-voice-is-being-converted-to-text-digital-art.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-808\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>There are many factors to consider when picking the best online consultation app for doctors. Some of these factors include: 1. The app&#8217;s features &#8211; Does the app have all the features you need? For example does the app have a voice to text because that saves a doctors time. 2. The app&#8217;s ease of&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/localhost:8000\/index.php\/best-online-